          "commentType": "CATALYTIC ACTIVITY",
          "reaction": {
            "name": "(S)-4-amino-5-oxopentanoate + tRNA(Glu) + NADP(+) = L-glutamyl-tRNA(Glu) + NADPH + H(+)",
